description: Defense attorneys for Bryan Kohberger, the man accused of killing four college students in Idaho, are asking a judge to order the prosecution to share more evidence in their case.
title: Bryan Kohberger defense challenges Idaho prosecutors over cellphone records

description: An attorney said the remaining wrongful death lawsuit filed after the 2021 Astroworld music festival has been settled; a deadly crowd crush at the festival left 10 people dead.
title: Remaining wrongful death lawsuit filed after deadly Astroworld concert has been settled, lawyer says

description: The Environmental Protection Agency rejected Thursday a proposal by Alabama to take over coal ash regulation, citing insufficient protections in the state plan.
title: EPA shoots down Alabama coal ash regulation proposal

description: The NBA has reportedly closed its investigation of Oklahoma City Thunder guard Josh Giddey, who was alleged to have a relationship with a minor in November.
title: NBA closes investigation into Thunder’s Josh Giddey over underage relationship allegations: report

description: A Turkish migrant crossing the border illegally into the United States told Fox News he thinks Americans should be concerned about there being "no security."
title: Turkish migrant crossing US border says Americans are 'right' to be concerned: 'No security'

description: The Coast Guard on Thursday suspended its search for three people who went missing after their boat capsized near Aialik Bay, Alaska, a day earlier.
title: Coast Guard suspends search for 3 people missing after boat capsized in Gulf of Alaska bay

description: U.S. Marshals tracked down and arrested Lee George-Maldonado in Connecticut for allegedly murdering a man in Fall River, Massachusetts in December.
title: US Marshals nab fugitive in Connecticut, wanted for murder and other crimes in Massachusetts

description: New York Gov. Kathy Hochul called Trump supporters “clowns" on Thursday during a media appearance ahead of the former president’s New York City rally in the Bronx.
title: New York Gov. Kathy Hochul calls Trump supporters ‘clowns’ in her own 'basket of deplorables' moment

description: Chris Hemsworth acknowledged his wife's never-ending support of his career, thanking her for putting her own career aside to champion his.
title: Chris Hemsworth 'forever' in wife's 'debt' after she ‘put aside her own dreams’ to support his

description: Defense officials from Chile met in Antarctica in an attempt to bolster their territorial claims in the southernmost continent, amid escalating tensions over Russia's maneuvers in the region.
title: In message to Russia, Chilean lawmakers meet in Antarctica to underline territorial claims

description: The New England Aquarium is warning Cape Cod beachgoers to beware of sharks ahead of the Memorial Day weekend after marine animals were spotted with shark bites.
title: Sharks spotted off popular Memorial Day weekend getaway spot

description: Céline Dion nearly died during her battle with a rare neurological disorder, stiff person syndrome. The Grammy Award-winning singer was diagnosed in 2022.
title: Céline Dion 'almost died' during stiff person syndrome battle

description: A Capitol Hill staffer used an umbrella to obstruct a Fox News cameraman who was filming Chad Pergram's interview with Rep. Rashia Tlaib.
title: Hill aide interferes with Fox News camera crew during Tlaib interview

description: A destructive EF-4 tornado killed four people and injured at least 35 in the small city of Greenfield, Iowa; more than 100 homes in the community of 2,000 were ripped apart in just one minute.
title: More bad weather could hit Iowa, where 3 powerful tornadoes caused millions in damage

description: In an unprecedented move, the NCAA and its five power conferences have agreed to allow schools to make direct payments to players for the first time in the history of college sports.
title: NCAA to allow Power 5 conferences to pay players in unprecedented agreement

description: Thousands of people rallied for former President Donald Trump in the Bronx's Crotona Park, one of New York City's deepest-blue areas.
title: Trump vows to 'save' deep-blue New York City in massive, historic Bronx rally
